title: Grateful Dead Live at Soldier Field on 1993-06-19
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Grey, Little Red Rooster, Lazy River Road, Me & My Uncle-> Maggie's Farm, Broken Arrow, Deal

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Way To Go Home-> Truckin'-> Smokestack Lightning-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Standing On the Moon-> Throwing Stones-> One More Saturday Night, E: Rain

Sting opened
